  "subject": "Remove legacy dependencies",
  "commit_message": "Remove legacy dependencies\n\nRemove the following dependencies (will be removed in other repos):\n- commons-beanutils\n- commons-io\n- commons-net\n- commons-text\n- guava\n- net.jimblackler.jsonschemafriend\n- org.json\n- plexus-utils\n\nAlso exclude transitive dependencies from other onap components,\nwhich re-include the above and other vulnerable dependencies.\n\nIssue-ID: POLICY-5592\nChange-Id: I9a4fdb3e0177d32a57b1e7f980af08ca7d81b74a\nSigned-off-by: danielhanrahan <daniel.hanrahan@est.tech>\n",
